msgstr "Conclusione"

#: data/help.cfg:192
msgid "This concludes the fundamentals of Wesnoth. You might want to read up on Basic Strategy, or familiarise yourself with <ref>dst=traits text=Traits</ref> and <ref>dst=abilities text=Abilities</ref>, but you now know everything you need to know to play the Heir to the Throne scenario. Have fun, and good luck!"
