#: data/scenarios/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/End_Of_Peace.cfg:97
#, fuzzy
msgid "Look, companions!  Those orcs don't imagine they are living their last day.  Let's slay all of them and give this land back to our people!"
msgstr "Guardate compagni! Questi orchi non s'immaginano che stanno vivendo i loro ultimi giorni. Uccidiamoli tutti e rendiamo questa terra alla nostra gente!"

#: data/scenarios/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/End_Of_Peace.cfg:102
#, fuzzy
msgid "We are attacked by these humans!  Hurry up, we must defend our fathers' land!"
