#: data/scenarios/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/Shan_Taum_The_Smug.cfg:188
#, fuzzy
msgid "This is true.  Now we are pressured from all sides by humans and elves; we need a leader that can unite all banners.  This one is YOU!"
